title: Bug 4121 - JarExporter causing out of sync issue
description: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported jar file the second time.
OB: When overwriting the exported jar file the second time, an out of sync message is displayed.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself to prevent the out of sync issue.
SR:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Place the exported jar file in the same directory (project).
3. Overwrite the exported jar file with a new version.
4. Observe the out of sync message.
